%h1 Turbo Linter Examples

%p Enable the <strong>Turbo Linter</strong> in the DevTools panel to see errors highlighted in red.

%section
  %h2 Valid Turbo Frames
  %turbo-frame#valid-frame
    %p This frame has a proper id.
  %turbo-frame#another-frame
    %p Another valid frame.

%section
  %h2 Valid data-turbo-frame reference
  %a{href: "/haml", data: {turbo_frame: "valid-frame"}} Load into valid-frame

%hr

%h2 Errors below (should be caught by the linter)

%section.error-example
  %h2 Frame without id
  %turbo-frame
    %p This turbo-frame is missing the required id attribute.

%section.error-example
  %h2 Reference to non-existent frame
  %a{href: "/haml", data: {turbo_frame: "does-not-exist"}} Load into missing frame

%section.error-example
  %h2 Another dangling reference
  %form{action: "/haml", data: {turbo_frame: "ghost-frame"}}
    %button Submit to non-existent frame
